{"tid":2390003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇：強制檢測不是侵犯人權","createTime":"2021-02-01T09:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T17:07:40.000Z","uid":19552,"like":8,"dislike":322,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"ec4845723412ed12fa1c438f732a1cb772f61894","tid":2390003,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:21:08.000Z","msg":"港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇表示，私家醫生交回的病人樣本新冠病毒陽性比例高，認為有病徵患者沒有及時檢測，令病毒在社區繼續傳播，他又認為強制檢測和人權無關。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇：「迫你去驗病毒就是侵犯人權，其實不是這樣，我們每個人都沒有免疫，如果每個人不合作，有病徵病狀又不去測試，傳播鏈就不會中斷，這和政治和人權真的是無關。機場檢測陽性比例0.35%是陽性反應，但你是否知道，私家醫生那裡有病徵病狀取去測試的，是0.72至0.8%陽性，較機場更高。我重申，我們其中防疫措施有很大的漏洞，是有病徵病狀的人不是全部去接受測試，以致隱性傳播鏈沒有辦法中斷。」"},{"pid":"b695a7d5e8a9908358f108dd1e25ae5188577947","tid":2390003,"uid":1354,"like":43,"dislike":3,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:21:38.000Z","msg":"想私鳥牠"},{"pid":"f4b56c773741790c3956bdf3fdb9a448cbecb397","tid":2390003,"uid":228143,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"佢似瘟神  風水佬 白卡佬多d"},{"pid":"9c619b1055282e05eed39083695aefb20ebed5c7","tid":2390003,"uid":33099,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:23:57.000Z","msg":"袁國勇玩過肛拭子未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d763bb512e02e74280084bb73323c8d196fdf63","tid":2390003,"uid":76804,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6cg2oCQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6cg2oCQ.png&h=babde169&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03e45208c859b9a4fe1c20d3dcab3f4fc9c32fbe","tid":2390003,"uid":224533,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PruO3C3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPruO3C3.png&h=4340f73e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.